          <h2>About</h2>

          <p>
            Literally Canvas is an extensible, BSD-licensed, HTML5 drawing
            widget that currently supports a minimal set of drawing operations.
            You can draw, erase, set the color with the eyedropper, undo, redo,
            pan, and zoom.
          </p>

          <p>
            The project will always depend on
            <a href="http://jquery.com/">jQuery</a> and
            <a href="http://underscorejs.org/">Underscore.js</a>. At the moment,
            it also depends on a small subset of
            <a href="http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap">Twitter Bootstrap</a>
            which is being phased out.
          </p>
